title: Annuar: I was not informed to testify before Mara audit committee
text:
More 
Suspended Mara chairperson Annuar Musa said he was not informed about testifying before the Mara audit committee today. 
"I have no idea. I was never called nor informed. You need to ask Mara," he said when contacted. 
He said this in response to Mara interim chairperson Yusof Yacob who yesterday said Annuar would be called before the Mara audit committee today.
